  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>On DASH Planet, King Slap kept all his shiny gems to himself. Everything was peaceful... until the heroes showed up, jumping on heads, shooting wildly, blowing up crates, and snatching diamonds!</strong><br><strong>Unleash your creativity and speed! Enter DASH Planet, gear up, and build insane levels packed with:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed streaks & (extreme) precision platforming</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enemies, crates, platforms, power-ups & spikes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Humiliating head jumping & heavy explosives</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-bending puzzles & action-packed arenas</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Double jumping, bullet jumping, wall sliding & triple dashing!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/9e5a7072c1887b913550a3c5df21ea80.poster.avif?t=1762692330\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/9e5a7072c1887b913550a3c5df21ea80.webm?t=1762692330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/9e5a7072c1887b913550a3c5df21ea80.mp4?t=1762692330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your world, your rules</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design puzzle, runner, hardcore precision, or any genre levels in the level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore pixelated tilesets and backgrounds to craft your story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go horizontal or vertical—the choice is yours</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play, share, compete</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills with gamepad or keyboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upload unlimited levels for the world to play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your arenas become hot spots for speedrunners</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Global competition</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt for shiny, colorful diamonds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your precision skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five unique characters, each with their own strengths</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shave off milliseconds and stay on top!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the fastest player's replay ghost</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worldwide leaderboards: world records, completed levels, and top creators</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Player vs Player mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/2533e7e697cbfb5baea36d5d6316c387.poster.avif?t=1762692330\" width=598 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/2533e7e697cbfb5baea36d5d6316c387.webm?t=1762692330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/898910/extras/2533e7e697cbfb5baea36d5d6316c387.mp4?t=1762692330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Creative Community</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build, share, and track your levels to see your worth as a creator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online level hub showing user ratings, clearance rates, plays, and high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create playlists, share them, and explore dynamic daily levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join a live Discord community — speedrunners, streamers, and creators united</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Show off your skills. Share your worlds. Become a DASH legend.</strong></p>",
